{"tid":2313951,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"丁月之災","createTime":"2020-12-06T07:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T05:43:37.000Z","uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d38dd053b11ad535e1a88b2a785aca7fb2b644","tid":2313951,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T07:54:03.000Z","msg":"上年丁丑月：疫情開始<br />\n<br />\n今年丁亥月：疫情反彈<br />\n<br />\n推斷原因：<br />\n肺屬辛金亦等於酉金為陰金<br />\n陰金最怕陰火 (丁火 / 巳火)<br />\n所以一見丁火即火熔金<br />\n<br />\n未來潛在危機：<br />\n如果推論冇錯，聽日 (6/12) 疫情又會開始慢慢好轉返。<br />\n<br />\n出年辛丑年，辛金流年出干，丙申月流年開始受剋，衰到庚子月回氣。<br />\n<br />\n出年 5/3 - 4/4 流月出干，又會有可能爆多波，但只係細波，一個月內完。<br />\n<br />\n而如果去到出年 7/8 前疫情都控制得唔好，7/8 - 7/12 較大機會又嚟大爆發。"},{"pid":"fbc60376872326dc68a6ec317e7faaf627210177","tid":2313951,"uid":18012,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"神棍又鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a81948daee174419d7b4905f8cf544bb662b977","tid":2313951,"uid":182624,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:09:59.000Z","msg":"又話林鄭3,4月收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7f8317dad0fd9e49db7f79f3018f5b61f2bbc5","tid":2313951,"uid":106,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:29:41.000Z","msg":"咁香港下年會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c49896930aff0ce859befb77ed8c905683de60","tid":2313951,"uid":17330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"股市點睇？"},{"pid":"8a592ff912040bde1a05d87d78497bf942d2eac4","tid":2313951,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T10:33:13.000Z","msg":"永續武炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmo